https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Xfce


(1) Make an Application menu item

Add a file of type .desktop to ~/.local/share/applications

as follows:

Example let's saz I want ot add Eclipse 4 Scala

[Desktop Entry]
Version=1.0
Type=Application
Name=Eclipse Kepler Scala
Icon=/home/rosemary/programming/scala/eclipse/eclipse-standard-kepler-SR2_Scala/scala_logo.png
Exec=/home/rosemary/programming/scala/eclipse/eclipse-standard-kepler-SR2_Scala/eclipse
Comment=Develop with pleasure!
Categories=Development;IDE;
Terminal=false
StartupNotify=true
StartupWMClass=EclipseScala


